The only prerequesite for this program is the Linux dialog command and it can be installed from Ubuntu or CentOS from the following commands:

APT-based distros:
"apt-get install dialog"

RPM-based distros:
"yum -y install dialog"

LBNL 'cf' tool
wget ftp://ee.lbl.gov/cf.tar.gz
tar zxvf cf.tar.gz
cd cf-1.2.5/
./configure
make;make install
